org.eclipse.gef4.common.adapt.inject

Class AdapterMaps

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.gef4.common.adapt.inject.AdapterMaps

  • public class AdapterMaps
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class to obtain a MapBinder, via which adapter (map) bindings can be specified in a Module.

        Returns a MapBinder, which is bound to an AdapterMap annotation of the given type, and can thus be used to specify adapter that are to injected into IAdaptables of the respective type.

        binder - The Binder used to create a new MapBinder.
